.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH DELPHI-MATTE 1  "delphitools-cli 0.1.0" "delphitools manual"
.SH NAME
matte \- Place a non\-square image on a square (or aspect\-ratio) matte
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBmatte\fR [\fB\-\-ratio\fR] [\fB\-\-mode\fR] [\fB\-\-colour\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fIIMAGES\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Place a non\-square image on a square (or aspect\-ratio) matte
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-ratio\fR \fI<RATIO>\fR [default: 1:1]

.TP
\fB\-\-mode\fR \fI<MODE>\fR [default: blur]
Matte fill mode: solid, blur, gradient
.TP
\fB\-\-colour\fR \fI<COLOUR>\fR [default: #ffffff]
Background colour (for \-\-mode solid)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
[\fIIMAGES\fR]

